item.title: CVE-2021-38432|2024-08-04T01:44:22.258Z -- fatek%20automation -- communication%20server
item.description: FATEK Automation Communication Server Versions 1.13 and prior lacks proper validation of user-supplied data, which could result in a stack-based buffer overflow condition and allow an attacker to remotely execute code.
